  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Slavers_Bay.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Black Cliffs is located in Slaver&#39;s Bay\"><img alt=\"Black Cliffs is located in Slaver&#39;s Bay\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Slavers_Bay.png/300px-Slavers_Bay.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Slavers_Bay.png/450px-Slavers_Bay.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/Slavers_Bay.png/600px-Slavers_Bay.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 27.8%; left: 50%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Black Cliffs\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Black Cliffs</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> and the location of the Black Cliffs\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Black Cliffs</b> are a series of cliffs that are situated on the northwest coast of <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a>, south of the <a href=\"/index.php/Painted_Mountains\" title=\"Painted Mountains\">Painted Mountains</a>. They lie between <a href=\"/index.php/Tolos\" title=\"Tolos\">Tolos</a> and the ruined city of <a href=\"/index.php/Bhorash\" title=\"Bhorash\">Bhorash</a>, south of the <a href=\"/index.php/Demon_Road\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Demon Road\">Demon Road</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Cliffs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Map_of_Valyria_(A_Dance_with_Dragons)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Map of Valyria (A Dance with Dragons)\">Map of Valyria</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403191914\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 574/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 3896/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3059/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1510/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 325/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   11.930      1 -total\n 84.97%   10.137      1 Template:Location_map\n 79.25%    9.454      1 Template:Location_map+\n 57.11%    6.813      1 Template:Location_map~\n 25.49%    3.042     22 Template:Location_map_Slavers_Bay\n  9.70%    1.157      1 Template:References\n  8.04%    0.959      3 Template:Location_map/decdeg\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:7204-0!ca